      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped leek</strong> to the dish with the<strong> chopped carrot </strong>and your<strong> baby button mushrooms</strong> and stir it all together</p><p>Add your <strong>beef stock mix</strong>, 450ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[600ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[750ml]</span><strong> boiled water </strong>and a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Bring to the boil then cover with the lid and put the dish in the oven for an initial 55 min</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1703861505198-x200.jpg",
