    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After an initial 55 min, add your<strong> gochujang </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!),<strong> sesame oil</strong> and <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> to the stew</p><p>Stir it all together, cover with the lid and return to the oven for a final 5 min – this is your<strong> oven-baked spicy Korean-style beef & leek stew</strong></p>",
